  "texts": [
    "Using the concept of autopoiesis, we can see that there is a mutual dynamic in the relationship between this technology and the author.",
    "Generative AI will not produce meaningful text for the scientific system without the author or individual engaged with a certain scientific field.",
    "It is not about the capabilities of LLMs alone but about engaging with this kind of technology throughout the scientific communication and the praxis of scientists, who serve as a structural coupling between the scientific system and the psychic system (individual) in the process of knowledge production.",
    "This structural coupling implies that scientists and generative AI are interconnected in a way that neither can fully function in the realm of scientific authorship without the other.",
    "The generative AI provides the raw capabilities for text generation, but it is the scientist who directs, refines, and contextualizes this output within the framework of existing scientific knowledge and methodologies."
  ],
